ing-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/coleslaw-dressing.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-how-to-make-coleslaw\"\u003eHow to Make Coleslaw\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eFinely shred the cabbage. 